{"tid":2192642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"🟊世碩電子派發員工證拋落地下，員工需彎腰執有如賤民！","createTime":"2020-09-07T08:56:02.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T05:50:19.000Z","uid":38539,"like":176,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"997ea467ab68ce54d075e5849a625b4363cb7089","tid":2192642,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T08:56:02.000Z","msg":"近日，有網友爆料，世碩電子（崑山）公司一男子派發員工證件時隨手扔在地下，員工需低頭彎腰才能拾起。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/a9qp0JW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fa9qp0JW.jpg&h=f9e15356&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kMYbFJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkMYbFJM.jpg&h=af1097ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cyEqLbQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcyEqLbQ.gif&h=09421989&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  視頻經曝光後引發衆怒，有網友認爲該公司涉嫌歧視員工。隨着輿論的發酵，該公司在9月5日晚發佈聲明稱，是單位管理人員失職，主管將率團隊向員工緻歉。<br />\n<br />\n  但緊接着的第二天，有媒體發佈的視頻顯示，員工證扔地事件發生後，該公司出現員工集體性離職，3000名員工已有2900名離開。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZS9NYwE.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZS9NYwE.gif&h=c0108e42&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  公司門口排起了長長的隊伍，基本都是員工們前來辦理離職手續。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taDyT44.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaDyT44.gif&h=68650087&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1268e44832307401f8ed2799ba2a66cf6c3f307","tid":2192642,"uid":222970,"like":109,"dislike":1,"score":108,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wNsPsvh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwNsPsvh.jpg&h=2bd481ac&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKBwFQi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKBwFQi.jpg&h=fbf762bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ke1c9JE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKe1c9JE.jpg&h=b07e7739&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/R5PFzaj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FR5PFzaj.jpg&h=605350b1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bd1441033cdf4f5bae8cf291c6d50a1d53240779","tid":2192642,"uid":38539,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:02:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JdxWRWO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJdxWRWO.png&h=5d4bb442&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evOK0P8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevOK0P8.png&h=c15bc377&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e26b9806c769d60680c09f541c931acc480e220","tid":2192642,"uid":256783,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:04:20.000Z","msg":"用口擔起佢, 再搖兩下尾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30c855dda588f0aacfb657da64e0a63a4f24e0d2","tid":2192642,"uid":15605,"like":148,"dislike":3,"score":145,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:17:12.000Z","msg":"明明就係支那人狗咬狗，係要拉台灣人落水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8acf8ada816b3b659dcfddfb2a12074c1987b3e","tid":2192642,"uid":273218,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:18:22.000Z","msg":"果然係下賤民族"},{"pid":"c617676b494c2e45bdbb16a6dae40d2445a26685","tid":2192642,"uid":85586,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:23:51.000Z","msg":"踐踏完又點<br />\n夠撚膽罷工拆咗間廠咩<br />\n咪又繼續汪汪叫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa26827ab7c57767367962bf347a3e2328f4e706","tid":2192642,"uid":282637,"like":136,"dislike":1,"score":135,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T09:29:02.000Z","msg":"<del>該公司出現員工集體性離職</del>該公司員工集體離職"},{"pid":"9897652ff8c89394233b33bad5eac5a66bdbd86f","tid":2192642,"uid":34383,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"p